            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot (with a matching lid) over a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]<strong> </span>flour</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further or until a sandy paste forms – this is your <strong>roux</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
