        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chicken stock</strong>, <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>, and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the pot<strong> </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for an initial 10-12 min or until the potatoes are almost cooked through</p>",
