    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>shredded kale</strong> and shake off any excess water</p><p>Trim, then chop your<strong> green beans</strong> in half</p><p>Once the potatoes are almost cooked through, add the <strong>shredded kale </strong>and<strong> halved green beans</strong> to the pot and cook, covered, for a further 2-3 min or until tender</p>",
