    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the<strong> cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>butter beans</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>pulled chicken</strong>, your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong> and your <strong>soft cheese</strong></p><p>Stir everything together – this is your <strong>chicken & butter bean stew</strong></p>",
